properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 17 at 9:20PM CST until January 18 at 6:00AM CST by NWS Hastings NE
properties.description:
...HIGH WIND WARNING EXPANDED TO INCLUDE ADAMS AND CLAY
COUNTIES...

* WHAT...Northwest winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts of 50 to 60 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Adams and Clay Counties.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to 6 AM CST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Damaging winds could blow down trees and power lines.
Isolated power outages are possible. Travel will be difficult,
especially for high profile vehicles.
properties.instruction:
People should avoid being outside around trees and branches. If
possible, remain in the lower levels of your home during the
windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM CST SATURDAY
